profile: Country Green Excavating is a full service commercial and residential excavation contractor, operating out of the Fraser Valley and Greater Vancouver Areas. Covering all aspects of single family residential excavation and landscaping such as: foundation excavations, back-filling and service upgrades, pool excavations, structurally engineered retaining walls, decorative retaining walls, concrete forming, and septic systems. Country Green also operates as a full service multi family residential and commercial excavation contractor providing services such as: subdivision development, underground mainline utility instillation (storm, sanitary, water), underground electrical and communications instillation's (hydro, telus, shaw, streetlighting), bulk excavations, land clearing, pre loads, demolition, remediation and environmental, and structural retaining walls. Country Green has the equipment and personnel to take on any project whether it be a small back yard retaining wall or a multi unit townhouse development.
